These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different games are played: snooker, canasta, backgammon
1. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
2. the person playing backgammon is between the person playing snooker and the person playing canasta##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Game   | snooker | backgammon | canasta |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, march, september
1. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in september##2
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Birthday   | september | december | march |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: garlic, blueberry, cabbage
1. the person eating blueberry is between the person eating garlic and the person eating cabbage##2
2. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person eating garlic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Food   | cabbage | blueberry | garlic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-4::.
City: marseilles, london, edinburgh
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the person traveling to london and the person traveling to marseilles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |     3      |
| City   | marseilles | edinburgh | london |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
3 different pets are kept: dog, pony, goat
1. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the pony##2
2. the owner of the goat is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Pet   | pony | dog | goat |

 #################################

 
